latestIgtvVideos.title: Pataa App
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@pataa_app is one stop solution for all your addressing issues. 
This app is helping a lot to the mass in these tough times of COVID-19, as people do not prefer going out of their houses for the daily gigs so they get everything at their doorstep, with this app you can save massive amount of time and energy of yours and the delivery person, this app helps significantly for navigations. 

Here are some of its really cool features -

1. Shortcode 
It has a shortcode feature that makes your long address into a customized smart code and solves the issue of long addressing, the user only has to share the code through the link and the receiver will know the entire address so you don't write it again and again.

2. Voice Direction 
This app supports voice directions, to explain details of the destination, you can record and share the precise details with the person like parking space details, floor number, pets awareness, etc, over the app. This will minimize the micro-management multiple times.

3. Accuracy 
This app is guaranteed on-point for location accuracy. Tried and tested. It drops your location pin at the gate of your house which makes it extremely accurate and directed.

4. Photos & Remarks - 
One of the most helpful perks of this app is that it allows you to share the house photos and remarks along with it and it can be shared with the respective person in the same customized shortcode

5. One-Click Game -
Sharing Address made easy with just one click -  even if your visitor doesn't have Pataa app then they can look at your Pataa details with help of the shared weblink.

🚨 All the emergency services will be reachable extremely easily like ambulance, police, etc.

https://app.pataa.com/infl

#Pataa #AddressingRevolution #KaroPataa #Pataa #YehRahaApnaPataa #TiltThisWay #Collab
